WEBVTT

00:00:05.996 --> 00:00:07.496
Do you sleep restlessly?

00:00:07.538 --> 00:00:09.621
Are you irritable or moody?

00:00:09.663 --> 00:00:11.079
Do you forget little things?

00:00:11.121 --> 00:00:13.788
Or do you feel overwhelmed and isolated?

00:00:13.829 --> 00:00:16.913
Well, do not worry.
We all experience this.

00:00:16.954 --> 00:00:19.079
You are probably just stressed out.

00:00:19.121 --> 00:00:21.663
But stress is not always a bad thing.

00:00:21.704 --> 00:00:24.746
It can be useful to boost
energy and concentration

00:00:24.788 --> 00:00:27.579
when participating
in a sports competition for example,

00:00:27.621 --> 00:00:29.538
or having to speak in front of a public.

00:00:29.579 --> 00:00:31.204
